{"tid":924064,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我同女朋友扑扑下野果陣條賓州唔見左","createTime":"2018-12-01T18:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T06:46:50.000Z","uid":212399,"like":19,"dislike":643,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"07980a51a6c374a5683ad1d48560d3d6b2c8830e","tid":924064,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:36:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的，前排去女朋友屋企過夜，本身個人好攰，唔想扑野，但係女朋友話好想要，咁我就承全佢。<br />\n我除哂佢D衫然後推佢落床，然後我㩒住佢黎屌，愈屌愈快屌到佢反白眼，然後神奇既事發生喇，我下面忽然間冇哂感覺，條女問我係咪抽左岀黎，我心諗都就黎射點會抽岀黎啊，你估拍AV咩，原來我條賓州唔見左，但係個春袋重係到，條女問咁點算好<br />\n1)係屋企搵，可能跌左落地下呢<br />\n2)唔見野緊係報失啦，重諗"},{"pid":"c1e083044579cea01c1d746b6db7cf82f62fa30a","tid":924064,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea21b3c5d59cc106bb79004109419e95a1140f6","tid":924064,"uid":177841,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:37:41.000Z","msg":"伊頓亨特"},{"pid":"e3c3b2f387272759617a30d62da16038ab0a4985","tid":924064,"uid":2901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:37:56.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"280744ff09ead3caaafd37fe19729744492f9e5c","tid":924064,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dea21b3c5d59cc106bb79004109419e95a1140f6","tid":924064,"uid":177841,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:37:41.000Z","msg":"伊頓亨特"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8b92d8aa26ba845f2cd23453aa7d2edd48f152","tid":924064,"uid":135169,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:38:11.000Z","msg":"請勿靠近車門"},{"pid":"c74806005f531f4f0b04ba2eba53836bb9447d7f","tid":924064,"uid":55956,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:38:19.000Z","msg":"小心有牙"},{"pid":"ab8c2b21f1fba739e081d6d0e15b53409be2d9fa","tid":924064,"uid":216727,"like":155,"disl